gorbachev reportedly is scheduled to spend three days in 
lithuania this week trying to heal the rift between the republics 
breakaway communist party and moscow on dec 20 a majority of 
lithuanian communists voted to break ties with the national party 
a possible precursor to secession by the baltic republic of 37 
million people 
