sajudis call for the rally 
sajudis intends for gorbachev to see for himself that there is 
no alternative for lithuania besides independence he said 
nationalist rallies in the more politically active of the soviet 
unions 15 republics repeatedly have drawn hundreds of thousands 
an estimated 1 million residents of lithuania latvia and estonia 
joined hands last summer to protest the 1939 sovietnazi pact that 
allotted the baltic states to the soviet sphere 
the sajudis announcement calls for wednesdays demonstration to 
be peaceful dignified and disciplined vasiliauskas said 
there will be a few hundred thousand there thats for sure 
