nick never gave up even though steve went through a string of 
jobs and even stole a watch from another mentor joe and denied 
it nick would see steve several times a week work with his 
employers and sometimes even roust him from bed and drive him to 
work 
steve eventually became a reliable employee and avoided further 
arrests prompting a judge to give him a suspended twoyear 
sentence for his earlier offenses perhaps as significantly steve 
presented a new watch to joe and told nick i know ive never 
said this but i dont know where id be if it wasnt for you guys 
