said he has been in houston for several months visiting relatives 
he said california pacific international holdings co pte ltd the 
singaporebased parent firm of weatherby had been interested in 
buying bond corp for some time 
we had been looking for a lot of opportunities reynolds 
said we had a manager in singapore who had some relationship 
